nas con las que ha fluido todo e incluso más.'=>'Friendships and connections between people in general can be as deep as each of those involved wants them to be. Because there are friendships with whom not everything I have talked about before has come up, there are some with whom only some of those things have come up, there are some with whom everything has flowed and even more.','Lo importante es que cualquiera de estos componentes, <strong>no tiene </strong>por qué estar, sino que surgen genuinamente dentro de la conexión que se establece; sin esperar nada, sin expectativas, sin obligaciones… solo aceptando con los brazos abiertos lo que el otro desee darnos, cuando y como desee hacerlo.'=>'The important thing is that <strong>none of these</strong> components have to be there, but rather they genuinely arise within the connection that is established; without expecting anything, without expectations, without obligations... just accepting with open arms what the other wants to give us, when and how they want to do it.','Porque aquel pensamiento de “si somos amigos no podemos follar, y si follamos se pierde la amistad” es completamente retrógrado.'=>'Because that thought of “if we are friends we can\'t fuck, and if we fuck we lose the friendship” is completely retrograde.','Pues eso, en lo que yo quiero y de la forma en la que me vinculo, no me sirve.'=>'Well, that, in what I want and the way I relate, does not work for me.','Se pueden generar juegos, dinámicas, exploraciones que les hagan ser más vulnerables entre sí, que les lleven a conocerse más profundamente, o que les inviten a explorar de forma más erótica. <em>Vamos, que no todo es ir a un bar a tomar cerveza. </em>Podemos atrevernos a hacer cosas diferentes,<em><strong> ¡estamos en esta vida para experimentar!</strong></em>'=>'You can create games, dynamics, and explorations that make them more vulnerable with each other, that lead them to get to know each other more deeply, or that invite them to explore 